{"type":null,"faqId":11567,"title":"C8816D  WLAN待机的时候会自动断开，怎么解决，手机默认是什么设置？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">这个问题是休眠策略的问题。进入的方法：在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b><span>-&gt;<b>WLAN</b></span>，再点击<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=32874\" alt=\"\" />并进入<b>高级</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>在休眠状态下保持<span>WLAN</span>连接</b>，设置为“<b>始终</b>”。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">注：手机默认设置是<b>始终</b>，也就是一直连接。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">个选项的含义如下：<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">从不（会增加数据流量）</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">：屏幕关闭</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">分钟后进入休眠。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">仅限充电时</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">：只有在充电状态下才不进入休眠。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">始终</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">：一直不会进入休眠。<span></span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":3,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2351","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398501099000,"seriesProductName":"C8816D","visitedTimes":397,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"C8816D","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}